-- France Will Unveil Offshore Wind-Energy Policy by Year-End, Besson Says
-- B y   T a r a   P a t e l
-- 2010-12-01T10:27:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-01/france-will-unveil-offshore-wind-energy-policy-by-year-end-besson-says.html
French Industry Minister Eric Besson
said he will unveil details about offshore wind projects by the
end of the year. He also called for the solar industry to be
“better controlled” at a press conference in Paris today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
